- 5-phase workflow: Parallel Agent Strategy, Data Consistency, Figure/Table Audit, Cross-Reference Chain, Compile and Verify
- Checklist covering hardcoded numbers, \ref/\label/\input chains, \cite/.bib entries, placeholder text
- Verified on ProjectScylla Haiku ablation study paper

